      "content": "it's not just \"challenges\" though. it's everything. the debt, the loss of everything i built, the way everyone is going to look at me. it feels like there's no version of the future where i'm not just a walking embarrassment. i feel like i'm just waiting for the floor to fall out from under me completely.",
